   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">After Save</uicontrol> event is executed when you click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol> or <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save &amp; Continue</uicontrol> and the logic is executed after the record is saved.</p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">
         <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Use Case# Update information from current form to another form</uicontrol>
      </p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">If you want to update the details from the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Expenses</uicontrol> form into associated PO form, then you can use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">After Save</uicontrol> event to define the attributes.</p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">
         <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Use Case# Collect and consolidate the information from a different form, and update the information in the current form</uicontrol>
      </p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">In the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Contract Change Order</uicontrol> form, if you want to get the consolidated information from a field in the RFP form, and update a field in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">CHANGE ORDER</uicontrol> page, then you can use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">After Save</uicontrol> event to collect the appropriate information.</p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">
         <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Use Case# Define auto-generated numbering logic for a record</uicontrol>
      </p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">To define auto-generated numbering logic that requires information to be retrieved from Mind database, you can use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">After Save</uicontrol> event. For example, in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">BUDGET ESTIMATES</uicontrol> list page, if the numbering logic is calculated as follows:</p>
      <p product="Include_PG_Content" class="- topic/p ">Project Code - Project Type - Auto sequence number, then you can use the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">After Save</uicontrol> event to define the numbering logic.</p>
